# SPACED - Frontend MVP Checklist (v0.1)


— WEDGE ANCHOR —

Need a private place right now? Book a room near you in minutes.

Core moment:
Immediate need for discreet, short-duration private space.

————————————
Purpose

Track what is already implemented on the frontend and what still needs to be built next on frontend only.

---

Already done (frontend)

- [x] Landing page exists with SPACED branding and CTA buttons (`/`).
- [x] Nearby spaces discovery page exists (`/spaces`) with list view.
- [x] Space cards include type, distance, rating, and price.
- [x] Space detail page exists (`/spaces/[id]`) with:
  - [x] description
  - [x] amenities
  - [x] reviews
  - [x] pricing preview (30/60 min)
- [x] Booking page exists (`/book`) with booking form UI.
- [x] Duration selection supports 30 and 60 minutes.
- [x] Extension selection supports 15-minute increments (+15, +30).
- [x] Booking form validation exists (Zod + react-hook-form).
- [x] Local booking draft state exists (Zustand store).
- [x] Basic top navigation exists (Home, Spaces, Book, Login).
- [x] Mock inventory data exists for multiple spaces and use cases.
- [x] Upfront pricing is visible in discovery/detail/booking UI.

---

To build next (frontend only)

Critical for MVP completion (frontend)

- [ ] Add real frontend routes for auth pages in active app router:
  - [ ] `src/app/login/page.tsx`
  - [ ] `src/app/register/page.tsx`
- [ ] Build functional auth forms (submit states, field errors, success/error messages).
- [ ] Create booking confirmation page/UI after successful checkout.
- [ ] Add "access instructions" UI surface in booking confirmation/session screen.
- [ ] Add availability-first UX:
  - [ ] show only currently available spaces
  - [ ] clear labels for "available now" vs "next available"
- [ ] Add turnover buffer UX hints (15-30 min) in booking flow text and availability messaging.
- [ ] Improve discovery with location-focused UX:
  - [ ] nearby sort as default
  - [ ] quick filters for "instant access"
  - [ ] optional map/list toggle (map can be mocked first)
- [ ] Build extension flow UI during active session:
  - [ ] +15 min action
  - [ ] extension status feedback
- [ ] Add loading, empty, and error states across key pages (`/spaces`, `/spaces/[id]`, `/book`).
- [ ] Add basic i18n/language toggle (EN/ES) for key user flows.

Quality and consistency

- [ ] Replace remaining mixed-language copy with a consistent MVP language policy.
- [ ] Remove temporary/dev comments inside UI files.
- [ ] Ensure navigation links only point to routes that exist.
- [ ] Add frontend tests for core flows:
  - [ ] browse spaces
  - [ ] open detail
  - [ ] create booking intent
  - [ ] see confirmation state

---

Frontend out of scope for now (backend-dependent)

- [ ] Real payment processing UI states tied to backend responses.
- [ ] Real-time booking lock/conflict handling tied to backend availability APIs.
- [ ] Verified access-code retrieval from backend/session APIs.
